I'm a Jimmy Neutron fan. I like the characters and jokes. And this movie is realy cool and fun. We bought it for our son, but I think it's not his age yet (he's 5 now). Our son did enjoy this movie when he saw it. He laughed a lot when he saw it. But it's not one of his favorites. He only saw it two or three times. I think Jimmy Neutron is more for older kids, perhaps 7 to 10, or so. I on the other hand liked it a lot, so I'm sorry my son doesn't watch it. Because I really want to watch it, but I only watch movies and DVD's with him. I suspect especially boys will like it. I wouldn't buy it for 3 - 6 year olds, but for older kids, this certainly is a good one for the collection.

This is a great product to fill the gaps.  My little boy loves Jimmy Neutron, but its not always on when he's able to watch television.  So in the instances he wants to watch Neutron, I can through in this DVD and all is right in the universe.
